data.description: OFFERS DUE BY 8PM SATURDAY 4/13.  Welcome to this charming 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath colonial! As you step into the foyer, the gleaming hardwood floors invite you in, setting the tone for the elegance and comfort that awaits. The hardwood floors continue through into the dining room and throughout the second floor. The spacious dining room is filled with abundant natural light, creating an inviting ambiance for gatherings. The heart of the home, the gourmet kitchen, is a culinary enthusiast's dream, equipped with stainless steel appliances, including a double oven and gas range, granite counters, under cabinet and recessed lighting, and convenient pull-out drawers. The oversized center island and breakfast room provide the perfect setting for enjoying meals. Sliding doors lead to the deck overlooking the picturesque fenced-in backyard, ideal for outdoor relaxation and entertaining. Unwind in the step-down family room featuring a charming brick wood-burning fireplace that offers warmth and coziness on chilly evenings. The main floor also features a convenient powder room and an oversized laundry room for added functionality. Ascend to the second floor and retreat the primary bedroom suite, with hardwood floors, a rehabbed private bath, and a walk-in closet, providing a peaceful sanctuary to relax and rejuvenate. Three additional bedrooms and rehabbed hall bathroom complete the second floor, offering ample space for family and guests. With a two-car attached garage and plenty of driveway parking, convenience is at your fingertips. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful property your new home!
